# exe

**Type Property**

A type that represents a Windows executable.

## Declaration

```swift
static var exe: UTType { get }
```

## Discussion

The identifier for this type is `public.windows-executable`.

This type conforms to [doc://com.apple.uniformtypeidentifiers/documentation/UniformTypeIdentifiers/UTTypeData] and [doc://com.apple.uniformtypeidentifiers/documentation/UniformTypeIdentifiers/UTTypeExecutable].

## Executables

- **executable**: A type that represents an executable.
- **unixExecutable**: A type that represents a UNIX executable.
